\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cspan style\u003d\"color: #ff0000;\"\u003ePlease go to League Setup--\u0026gt;Teams and Schedules--\u0026gt;Schedule tab and make sure you have your desired season start/end dates set.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style\u003d\"color: #ff0000;\"\u003eFor H2H leagues, enable/disable\u0026nbsp;any merges you want (such as First 2 Periods, All-star break, Last 2 Periods). Then, go to Playoffs tab to set/check your league\u0027s Playoff Periods.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style\u003d\"color: #ff0000;\"\u003eAlso, be sure to go to Matchups tab after setting your Playoffs, to make sure all matchups are appearing for all regular season Periods. Regenerate matchups on that screen if necessary.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIt is VERY IMPORTANT you do this \u003cspan style\u003d\"color: #000000;\"\u003eprior to your league\u0027s draft, as you will not be able to change any dates afterwards\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEnjoy the season!\u003c/p\u003e","type":"3","title":"PLEASE READ - Essential Info for your MLB League","collapsible":true}]}}]}